                <head>397. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On July 11, <persName corresp="#p_HHF1">Holland</persName> forwarded a memorandum
                    to <persName>Dulles</persName>, entitled “Importance of Present United States
                    Relations With Argentina, Brazil and Chile.” The memorandum is printed as <ref
                        target="#d214">Document 214</ref>.</p>
